lead_paragraph: Sebastian Vettel has had better birthdays than the 29th he marked at the Austrian Grand Prix on Sunday, even if he could at least enjoy the warm glow of Germany's Euro 2016 soccer prowess over Italy the day before.

headline.print_headline: Vettel Has a Birthday to Forget
